玛恩纳送去的？","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_107"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_107","name2":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"佐菲娅","text":"......但他多半是不会理我的吧。再说我也不觉得他会按时换药......","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"佐菲娅","text":"虽然性格大相径庭，但有些地方，他和那姐妹俩还真像。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_107","name2":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"光头马丁","text":"我听说了，他和玛嘉烈正儿八经地进行了一场决斗，玛嘉烈赢了。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_107"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_107","name2":"avg_npc_101","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老工匠","text":"说不准这样才能让那个玛恩纳清醒一点......","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_101"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_120#3","name2":"avg_npc_101","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老骑士","text":"啧，我才不觉得那个小子有什么好清醒的，他清醒得很，太清醒了，才变成现在这副鬼样子。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_120#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"佐菲娅","text":"玛恩纳他......","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"佐菲娅","text":"......不，没什么。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"},{"type":"dialog","id":184},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":185},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_061#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":186},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛莉娅","text":"各位！啊，佐菲娅姐姐也在。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_061#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_061#2","name2":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"佐菲娅","text":"玛莉娅？你怎么一个人来了？","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_061#2","name2":"avg_npc_064_weapon_1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛莉娅","text":"刚才骑士协会的人来找姐姐，我就自己先过来了......","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_061#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛莉娅","text":"像姐姐这样曾被流放过，又重新取回身份的例子似乎不多，有很多法律文件要审查......","id"